## `POST /term/index`

Index the term as indicated in the JSON. 

### Return codes 

#### 200

Sample call

```bash
curl -v -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST http://localhost:8888/term/index -d '{
     "terms": [
         {
            "term": "मराठी",
            "frequency_base": 1.0,
            "frequency_stem": 1.0,
            "vector": [1.0, 2.0, 3.0],
            "synonyms":
            {
                "bla1": 0.1,
                "bla2": 0.2
            },
            "antonyms":
            {
                "bla3": 0.1,
                "bla4": 0.2
            },
            "tags": "tag1 tag2",
            "features":
            {
                "NUM": "S",
                "GEN": "M"
            }
	        },
		    {
            "term": "term2",
            "frequency_base": 1.0,
            "frequency_stem": 1.0,
            "vector": [1.0, 2.0, 3.0],
            "synonyms":
            {
                "bla1": 0.1,
                "bla2": 0.2
            },
            "antonyms":
            {
                "bla3": 0.1,
                "bla4": 0.2
            },
            "tags": "tag1 tag2",
            "features":
            {
                "NUM": "P",
                "GEN": "F"
            }
	        }
   ]
}'

```

